examples.en: Her paintings adorn the walls.
His paintings are without equal.
examples.ru: Его картины не имеют себе равных.

examples.en: His paintings are rather amateurish.
Her paintings never fail to fascinate.
These paintings exalt the imagination.
The paintings were consigned to our care.
examples.ru: Картины были переданы нам на хранение.

examples.en: She exhibited her paintings to the public.
He bequeathed his paintings to the museum.
examples.ru: Он завещал свои картины этому музею.

examples.en: The paintings were of the highest caliber.
He refused to give titles to his paintings.
examples.ru: Он отказался давать названия своим картинам.

examples.en: Turner's paintings give an effect of light.
The provenance of the paintings is unknown.
The paintings looked strangely out of place.
I thought the paintings were pretty ordinary.
The exhibition features paintings by Picasso.
The paintings are in an expressionistic style.
'Sunflowers' is one of his best-known paintings.
examples.ru: "Подсолнухи" — это одна из самых известных его картин.

examples.en: No one objected when the paintings were removed.
examples.ru: Никто не возразил, когда эти картины убирали.

examples.en: His paintings take their inspiration from nature.
examples.ru: Его картины черпают вдохновение из природы.

examples.en: He made a bequest of his paintings to the museum.
We hope for the recovery of the stolen paintings.
examples.ru: Мы надеемся на возвращение украденных картин.

examples.en: He pledged his paintings as collateral for a loan.
examples.ru: Он заложил свои картины в качестве гарантии по кредиту.

examples.en: He usually views abstract paintings with distaste.
examples.ru: Обычно он с отвращением смотрит на абстрактные картины.

examples.en: The paintings cost a great deal (=a lot) of money.
examples.ru: Эти картины стоят кучу (т.е. очень много) денег.

examples.en: They will be exhibiting a collection of paintings.
The museum has a matchless collection of paintings.
How do you react to this modern artist's paintings?
examples.ru: Как вы воспринимаете картины этого современного художника?

examples.en: The walls were cluttered with paintings and prints.
examples.ru: Стены были беспорядочно увешаны картинами и гравюрами.

examples.en: Has anyone traced the provenances of these paintings?
The family made a gift of his paintings to the museum.
examples.ru: Семья отдала его картины в дар музею.
